title: Default values are not displaying in Show Report Parameters dialog
description: Default values are not being shown in the Show Report Parameters dialog box.
OB: When I preview the report and click on the Show Report Parameters button, I observed that the default values are not being displayed in the value boxes.
EB: I expected to see the default values in the value boxes so that I could easily modify the parameter I wanted to change.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Preview the report
2. Click on the Show Report Parameters button.

Expected behavior:
- The default values should be displayed in the value boxes.

Observed behavior:
- In the Enter Parameters dialog box, all values are empty and I am unable to modify just one parameter. I have to input all the values again.
